| USAGE: SITE TAKE <user> <kbytes>[gGmM] <message>              |
|        (NOTE: The message part is optional)                   |
|                                                               |
| Example: SITE TAKE 1000 user                                  |
|          (This would take 1meg of credits from user.)         |
|          The g/m suffix is to specify gigabytes or megabytes  |
